data.description: Beautiful home on the hill in a quiet, established neighborhood with rocking chair front porch to enjoy overlooking your large yard! As you enter the home there is a double coat closet and half bath convenient for guests. Staircase in the entry leads upstairs to 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms and HUGE bonus room. Formal dining room. Kitchen with island and breakfast nook is open to the living room.  Living room has a gas log fireplace for those cold nights.  Step outside into the large, fenced backyard and enjoy a multi-level deck, firepit and HUGE 2-story outbuilding that is heated and cooled. Home exterior was painted  and both HVAC units in outbuilding were installed Jan 2023. Enjoy living with that country feel with only county taxes but so close to the highway, restaurants and shopping. Schools are Brier Creek, Brown and East Davidson. Come make this home YOURS TODAY!
